### Create Role - Admin (with all permissions)
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "admin",
  "description": "Administrator with full access",
  "permissionIds": [
    "PERMISSION_ID_1",
    "PERMISSION_ID_2",
    "PERMISSION_ID_3",
    "PERMISSION_ID_4",
    "PERMISSION_ID_5",
    "PERMISSION_ID_6",
    "PERMISSION_ID_7",
    "PERMISSION_ID_8",
    "PERMISSION_ID_9",
    "PERMISSION_ID_10"
  ]
}

###

### Create Role - Manager (users and products permissions)
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "manager",
  "description": "Manager with user and product management",
  "permissionIds": [
    "PERMISSION_ID_1",
    "PERMISSION_ID_2",
    "PERMISSION_ID_3",
    "PERMISSION_ID_5",
    "PERMISSION_ID_6",
    "PERMISSION_ID_7"
  ]
}

###

### Create Role - Sales (orders and products read)
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "sales",
  "description": "Sales representative with order and product access",
  "permissionIds": [
    "PERMISSION_ID_6",
    "PERMISSION_ID_9",
    "PERMISSION_ID_10"
  ]
}

###

### Create Role - Customer Service (read-only)
POST http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "customer_service",
  "description": "Customer service with read-only access",
  "permissionIds": [
    "PERMISSION_ID_2",
    "PERMISSION_ID_6",
    "PERMISSION_ID_10"
  ]
}

###

### Get All Roles
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/roles?page=1&limit=10

###

### Instructions:
# 1. First, run all requests in create-permissions.http to create permissions
# 2. Copy the permission IDs from the responses
# 3. Replace PERMISSION_ID_1, PERMISSION_ID_2, etc. with actual UUIDs
# 4. Then run the role creation requests above
#
# Permission mapping:
# PERMISSION_ID_1  = users:create
# PERMISSION_ID_2  = users:read
# PERMISSION_ID_3  = users:update
# PERMISSION_ID_4  = users:delete
# PERMISSION_ID_5  = products:create
# PERMISSION_ID_6  = products:read
# PERMISSION_ID_7  = products:update
# PERMISSION_ID_8  = products:delete
# PERMISSION_ID_9  = orders:create
# PERMISSION_ID_10 = orders:read
